/**
 * Maps an AppIcon enum value to the iOS Asset Catalog name (under the `Icons` namespace).
 * The names match the SVG filenames in /icons/ and the imageset names generated by
 * scripts/svg_to_imageset.py.
 *
 * If you add a new AppIcon enum value, add it here AND drop a matching SVG into /icons/.
 */
